  "title": "Laser-evoked potentials in the human spinal cord and cortex",
  "description": "This dataset comprises laser-evoked potentials recorded simultaneously from the human spinal cord and cortex. The study investigates nociceptive processing across multiple levels of the somatosensory system using high-resolution electrophysiological recordings. Data include EEG and spinal cord recordings from multiple subjects, providing insights into pain-related neural activity from peripheral to central nervous system levels.",
